metadata.name: Azuki 8480: Path of the Butterflies
metadata.description:
Disclaimer: 
This art work is based off ChipNFT's Azuki 8480. 
It is an art work created by me, placed in his Azuki Fan Art contest starting April 13, 2022!
With his permission under his contest thread, he is allowing artist submissions to be minted and sold ! 

Thank you for the opportunity to create a work consisting of a beautiful Azuki ! 

Dimensions: 3000 x 4000 px
300 DPI

This is my very first Derivative Artworks to be minted. I do not plan on minting many derivative artworks, so this is one of only a few!
